OL,3,CWarm weather and Mother's Day spending
OL,4,Cgives retailers March boost
OL,6,FThe improving weather made for a
OL,7,Fstrong final week, with gardening and
OL,8,FDIY equipment "flying off shelves",
OL,9,Fthe BRC said.
OL,11,FSales of jewellery and beauty products
OL,12,Fwere helped by Mother's Day, although
OL,13,Fconsumers remained more cautious about
OL,14,Fbuying bigger ticket items like
OL,15,Ffurniture.
