OL,7,Fare looking for UK-made alternatives
OL,8,Fto products they currently buy that
OL,9,Fare produced abroad.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, spending at garden centres
OL,12,Frose 13.4% ` the biggest spike
OL,13,Fincrease Barclays started tracking the
OL,14,Fcategory in January 2024.
OL,16,FJack Meaning, chief UK economist at
OL,17,FBarclays, said: "Following stronger-
